Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.81,0:00:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是問「你是不是在和塚本交往」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.87,0:00:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}交往？塚本…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.03,0:00:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊…你說秀一？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.93,0:00:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}究竟是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.64,0:00:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 我們沒在交往
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.47,0:00:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.42,0:00:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.56,0:00:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.61,0:00:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等等 為什麼要問這個問題？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.16,0:00:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒什麼 只是看你們常常一起回家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.59,0:00:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小綠我放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.36,0:00:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}葉月 上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.88,0:00:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}先等等 我昨天不是說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.99,0:00:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也不是喜歡塚本啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.04,0:00:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喜歡秀一？葉月嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.81,0:00:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}噓
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.23,0:00:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}都說了不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.28,0:00:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是你有點在意他吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.00,0:00:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這…這個嘛…一點點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.17,0:00:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}縣祭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.63,0:00:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有沒有想過「能跟他一起去就好了」之類的？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.61,0:00:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是有想過啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.50,0:00:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這就是戀愛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.77,0:00:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼要這麼刨根問底啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.53,0:00:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那當然是因為所有音樂都是始於戀愛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.65,0:01:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}愛情與生死是音樂永恆的主題
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.58,0:01:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就算說所有音樂都因它們而存在也不誇張喔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.02,0:01:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}葉月
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.77,0:01:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你的論點有點詭異吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.82,0:01:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來 上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.57,0:01:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等等 等等啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.49,0:01:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}說到縣祭就是每年6月5日舉辦的祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.25,0:01:15.42,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}※縣祭\N\h{\fscx80\fscy80}每年6月5日到6日在京都府宇治市舉行的祭典。{\r}\N\h{\fscx80\fscy80}叫縣祭是因為該祭典是宇治的平等院南門附近的縣神社的例祭。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.39,0:01:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}每到這時期 大家就會有點心神不寧的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就像這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.42,0:01:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}香織學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.68,0:01:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個 可以的話縣祭…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.24,0:01:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉 我已經跟明日香和晴香說好要一起去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.46,0:01:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就是要你別礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.96,0:01:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.12,0:01:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小綠要和妹妹一起去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.19,0:01:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 每年都是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.11,0:01:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是嗎 你們感情真好
Comment: 0,0:01:44.99,0:01:45.06,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,OP-FF FINAL
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.21,0:02:04.60,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}叶いたい事が　溢れてるから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.93,0:02:10.43,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}立ち止まってる　暇なんてないよね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.71,0:02:13.78,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}胸に秘めたあこがれを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.78,0:02:16.75,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}フルボリュームで届けよう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.76,0:02:21.68,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}行こう…クレッシェンドの向こうへ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.78,0:02:27.76,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}つまずいてもいい　はみだしてもいい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.76,0:02:36.24,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}君の音色を　僕たちは待っている
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.24,0:02:44.92,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}響け!　生まれたての夢つめ込んで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.06,0:02:50.86,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}大きな空へ　いま旅立とう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.86,0:02:56.54,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}拓け!　笑顔を味方につけて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.54,0:03:02.31,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}離さない　諦めたくない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.32,0:03:07.55,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}限界さえも　跳ね返す勇気で
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.87,0:03:11.80,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}DREAM SOLISTER
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.08,0:02:04.60,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}因為有太多心願
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.93,0:02:10.43,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}所以無暇停滯不前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.71,0:02:13.78,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}將心底秘藏的憧憬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.78,0:02:16.75,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}乘上最大的音量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.76,0:02:21.68,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}傳達到漸強記號的彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.78,0:02:27.76,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}遭遇挫折也好 合不上拍也罷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.76,0:02:36.24,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}我們都期待著你的美妙音色
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.24,0:02:44.92,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}奏響樂器 滿懷初生的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.06,0:02:50.86,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}向著廣闊天空 現在踏上旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.86,0:02:56.54,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}敞開胸懷 讓笑容成為夥伴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.54,0:03:02.31,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}不會放手 不願放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.32,0:03:07.55,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}鼓起勇氣 衝破界限
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.87,0:03:11.80,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}成為夢想的獨奏者
Comment: 0,0:03:11.80,0:03:13.80,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.28,0:03:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我會和班上同學去 然後跟著他們逛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.38,0:03:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}梨子學姐要跟誰一起去啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.61,0:03:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那還用說嗎 不就是和後藤嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.77,0:03:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等…夏紀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.90,0:03:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.31,0:03:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}學姐 難道這就是所謂的戀愛？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.96,0:03:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼戀愛不戀愛的 他們在交往呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.29,0:03:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}夏紀！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.11,0:03:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我興趣滿滿！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.86,0:03:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等等 還不知道算不算是在交往呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.57,0:03:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們沒有在交往嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.00,0:03:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.67,0:03:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是說了要保密的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.49,0:03:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.17,0:03:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}兩位終於按捺不住 要正式公開了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.15,0:03:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼針對這點來發表意見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.30,0:03:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為大家都知道 等到都急了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.67,0:03:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明日香學姐沒有男朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.35,0:03:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼可能有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.77,0:04:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我的戀人只有上低音號先生一個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.81,0:04:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}黃前要和誰去？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.48,0:04:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我嗎 我不太喜歡人多的地方啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.30,0:04:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}家又住在小吃街附近
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.53,0:04:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對逛祭典也興趣缺缺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.11,0:04:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}黃前對這種事就比較冷淡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.71,0:04:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.22,0:04:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}葉月要跟誰去？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.85,0:04:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.63,0:04:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哦 葉月啊…痛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.43,0:04:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還沒決定啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.49,0:04:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}祭典啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.94,0:04:29.81,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,0)\blur2\bord1.8\3c&HAA6D5B&\c&HFEFEFE&\pos(755,520)}祭典的三角鐵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.16,0:04:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}各位 我之前應該也有問過
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.28,0:04:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這部分究竟在表達什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.98,0:04:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}田中同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.68,0:04:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.29,0:04:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}「獨自離開地球 踏上前往遙遠星球的旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.63,0:04:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}月亮翩翩起舞 彷彿在為她的旅途祝福」這樣的畫面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.70,0:05:01.84,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}順帶一提 作曲者從小就最喜歡獨自眺望夜空…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.98,0:05:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}到這邊就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.04,0:05:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}田中同學剛剛的舞姿很不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.88,0:05:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要像那樣自由奔放 毫無羞澀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.47,0:05:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}將這一段音樂演奏得輕快而勇敢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.46,0:05:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}知道了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.67,0:05:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.39,0:05:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}黃前 這裡有點吃力嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.43,0:05:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.24,0:05:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這邊用替指可能比較適合
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.04,0:05:21.86,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}※替指（替え指）\N\h{\fscx80\fscy80}使用與基本運指不同的指法，發出與其相同的音高，使用替指有時可以簡化運​​指，達到更好的演奏效果。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.61,0:05:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.30,0:05:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那麼接下來從「柏林」的B樂段首開始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.09,0:05:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}單簧管先起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.16,0:05:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯…這樣 然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.22,0:05:33.85,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}唷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.62,0:05:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.33,0:05:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別無視我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.30,0:05:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還有擔心的地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.72,0:05:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.28,0:05:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.43,0:05:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}長號的人數很多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.07,0:05:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不加油點 試音就很難過了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.76,0:06:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}感覺如何
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.16,0:06:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一年級有三個人吹長號吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.39,0:06:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 還有福井和赤松
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.45,0:06:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}上低音號應該全都能通過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.99,0:06:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為人很少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.53,0:06:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但如果實力不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.84,0:06:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}感覺瀧老師他會毫不遲疑地把人換掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.21,0:06:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以不能鬆懈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.93,0:06:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}感覺我們真的能晉級全國大賽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.72,0:06:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然進入這裡的管樂社才兩個月左右
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.52,0:06:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}最近我卻有了這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.73,0:06:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}才沒這麼輕鬆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.23,0:06:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但一定比以前好不少了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.60,0:06:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.02,0:06:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真想更加進步啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.13,0:06:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對了 那下次一起來這裡練習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.62,0:06:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}上低音號好重 我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.58,0:06:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.34,0:06:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你5號有什麼計畫嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.55,0:06:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}5號？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.45,0:06:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}和平常一樣參加社團活動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.96,0:06:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是說在那之後
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.79,0:06:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可以跟我…一起去縣祭嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.88,0:07:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼 為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.71,0:07:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒什麼 考慮一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.34,0:07:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.36,0:07:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為這始料未及的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.67,0:07:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我的思考迴路完全亂成一團
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.47,0:07:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.47,0:07:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}根據推理
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.93,0:07:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}葉月想邀請秀一去縣祭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.40,0:07:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}而秀一想邀請我去…原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.17,0:07:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小綠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.33,0:07:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你這騙子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.34,0:07:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果是這樣的話為什麼不早點告訴我們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.63,0:07:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是啦 不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.20,0:07:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.35,0:07:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}久美子她…完全沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.64,0:07:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你別來火上加油了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.38,0:07:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這又是個麻煩啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.97,0:07:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.45,0:07:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那就必須行動了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.69,0:08:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}飛吧 跑吧 告白吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.10,0:08:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是 也許只是我會錯意了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.70,0:08:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}才沒有這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.21,0:08:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是吧 久美子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.42,0:08:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.09,0:08:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}葉月她啊 之前練習時和塚本同學眼神交…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.33,0:08:12.63,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喂—！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.04,0:08:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}綠輝 住口啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.57,0:08:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要叫我綠輝 太犯規了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.30,0:08:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}和秀一？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.18,0:08:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可能只是偶然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.49,0:08:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}才不是偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.12,0:08:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是必然 是命運
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.87,0:08:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對吧 久美子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.22,0:08:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎？嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.32,0:08:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}走吧 觀眾們也在等著曲目開始
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.79,0:08:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}上舞台吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.57,0:08:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}慢著慢著 到時候我自己去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.48,0:08:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我會自己去的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.13,0:08:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.85,0:08:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.61,0:08:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}赤松 抱歉 我有點事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.62,0:08:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好 上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.14,0:09:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哦 找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.17,0:09:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}幹嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.99,0:09:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我還想問你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.26,0:09:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你剛才不是打信號了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.46,0:09:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我？才沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.09,0:09:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼會沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.11,0:09:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你朝我看了眼 就一個人走出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.11,0:09:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這怎麼會變成信號了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.38,0:09:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一般都會這麼想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.36,0:09:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}說起來縣祭…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.57,0:09:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.08,0:09:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你有安排了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.80,0:09:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉 我要和這個人一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.13,0:09:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎 和高坂？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.69,0:09:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}塚本
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.01,0:09:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}能和你說幾句話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.92,0:09:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我正在和久美子說話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.76,0:09:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.01,0:09:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}去陪她一下吧 秀一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.27,0:09:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你就不介意？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.34,0:09:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.30,0:10:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.32,0:10:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.68,0:10:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}幾點在哪集合？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.19,0:10:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你說要一起去祭典的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.97,0:10:34.97,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\rDefault\blur2\bord0\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H000000&\pos(836,72)}長號
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.97,0:10:34.97,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\rDefault\c&HBDA40F&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(828,67)}長號
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.96,0:10:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我再說一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.73,0:10:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然是祭典 但是玩也要有高中生的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.98,0:10:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}知道了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.11,0:10:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聽完美智惠老師沒完沒了的叮囑後
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.19,0:10:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那麼今天的練習就到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.86,0:10:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}感謝指導
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.23,0:10:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}結束了因為祭典的氣氛而有點浮躁的練習
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.45,0:10:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}伴隨著黃昏 熱鬧的祭典時光到來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.13,0:11:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}久等了 後藤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.76,0:11:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.92,0:11:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.19,0:11:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可愛…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.38,0:11:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.28,0:11:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好了 葉月
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.31,0:11:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真的嗎 不會很奇怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.26,0:11:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}超可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.47,0:11:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我穿便服都沒怎麼穿過裙子…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.60,0:11:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是小綠耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.66,0:11:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還原度超高
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.59,0:11:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}經常有人這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.29,0:11:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}叫什麼名字呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.72,0:11:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.63,0:11:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這位是葉月
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.82,0:11:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}說晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.86,0:11:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.73,0:11:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}萌死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.95,0:11:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.91,0:11:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}姐姐 去祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.96,0:11:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這麼快就想去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.56,0:12:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那我們就先走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.98,0:12:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.65,0:12:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}葉月 你今天可愛極了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.35,0:12:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對吧 琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.80,0:12:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}超可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.04,0:12:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.46,0:12:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}棒透了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.60,0:12:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.32,0:12:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.92,0:12:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.77,0:12:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.67,0:12:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}加藤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.14,0:12:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉 來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.58,0:12:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.80,0:12:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.25,0:12:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}必須要把上低音號背來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.35,0:12:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你遲到了10分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.16,0:12:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.14,0:12:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.13,0:12:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒 可愛到我呆滯了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.87,0:12:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.13,0:12:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.52,0:13:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大吉山 要爬上去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.85,0:13:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.86,0:13:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就是想爬 樂器就交換著拿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.84,0:13:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}高坂同學那純白的連身裙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.88,0:13:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}和微涼的泛藍空氣 讓我看得入迷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.98,0:13:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}腦海中充滿了雪女的傳說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.78,0:13:18.62,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}※雪女\N\h{\fscx80\fscy80}日本傳說中的妖怪，山神的女兒{\r}\N\h{\fscx80\fscy80}在下雪的夜晚以美麗高挑的女子形象現身，下山引誘男人{\r}\N\h{\fscx80\fscy80}如果遇到她喜歡的，就會把他冰凍後帶回山裡。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.08,0:13:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}心懷一絲不安 卻還是被她的美麗所吸引而丟掉性命時的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.36,0:13:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大概就是這樣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.94,0:13:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你喜歡哪一個？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.30,0:13:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.44,0:13:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是剛才的神社 還是這邊的神社
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.67,0:13:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我更喜歡這邊的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.03,0:13:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}很素雅 老成而莊重
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.07,0:13:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你能體會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.53,0:13:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.45,0:13:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.58,0:13:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你經常這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.47,0:13:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.87,0:13:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}突然爬山什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.28,0:13:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你把我想成什麼怪人了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.41,0:13:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}當然不可能了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.41,0:13:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.87,0:14:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過 我有時候會想這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.37,0:14:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}穿著校服 上學 去管樂社 回家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.81,0:14:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有時會想拋下這一切
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.11,0:14:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}買張青春18車票踏上旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.90,0:14:11.03,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\fad(300,300)}※青春18是JR每年春、夏、冬發行三次的乘車券\N\h\h\h\h可以自由搭乘JR全線的普通車及部分海路航線的任意路線，並且可以在途中任意下車。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.62,0:14:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我想我有點能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.23,0:14:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}現在爬山就類似是替代那些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.91,0:14:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還真是降了不少等級
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.51,0:14:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒辦法 明天還得上學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.52,0:14:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.83,0:14:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}快來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.57,0:14:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}交換
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.56,0:14:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.29,0:14:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}樂器
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.47,0:14:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不用啦 這個挺重的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.41,0:14:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不行 不交換的話我心裡過意不去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.44,0:14:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.49,0:14:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}感覺有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.82,0:14:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.53,0:14:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}讓穿著白連身裙的你拿我的上低音號
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.24,0:14:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}超不道德啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.65,0:14:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.31,0:15:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}腳不痛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.20,0:15:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.35,0:15:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是我並不討厭疼痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.26,0:15:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這話感覺有點色
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.22,0:15:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}變態
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.94,0:15:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}希望試音一切順利
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.67,0:15:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你求這個也不會靈的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.54,0:15:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}話是這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.27,0:15:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}樂器和音樂明明都能靠自己的努力解決
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.18,0:15:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還來求神明 太浪費啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.26,0:15:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.45,0:15:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咦 那不是加藤嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.53,0:15:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還帶了男朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.65,0:15:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}加藤幹得好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.31,0:15:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不許追過去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.61,0:15:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要裝作沒看見 懂了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.01,0:15:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.15,0:15:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}終於能坐下了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.23,0:15:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來 章魚燒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.60,0:15:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過有點涼掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.29,0:15:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.63,0:16:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我還是第一次和男生一起逛縣祭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.75,0:16:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也是第一次和女生 還不太習慣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.80,0:16:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}加藤同學 低音號練得還順利嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.47,0:16:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}之前你還帶回家練吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.70,0:16:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}塚本 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.80,0:16:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.85,0:16:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 嗯…這個…哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.95,0:16:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你這是什麼反應啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.69,0:16:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只是…嚇了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.88,0:16:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那…回答呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.70,0:16:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.44,0:16:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.59,0:16:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好 我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.87,0:17:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我來幫忙撮合你和久美子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.63,0:17:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不…我對她沒有那種…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.35,0:17:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}難道你缺乏自覺？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.44,0:17:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真的沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.52,0:17:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}低音號…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.44,0:17:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}低音號的職責就是在背後默默支持
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.26,0:17:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}塚本同學！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.92,0:17:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}APP 我想會有點暗就裝了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.92,0:17:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我其實很早以前就在想了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.25,0:17:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}很想和你一起去玩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.27,0:17:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎！？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.84,0:17:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是久美子的個性很差吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.04,0:17:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}難道你是在批評我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.44,0:17:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是誇獎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.85,0:17:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}國三參加比賽時
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.15,0:17:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你問我「你真的覺得能進全國大賽嗎」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.78,0:17:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這不是個性很差嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.60,0:17:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 那只是我單純在意…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.28,0:18:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}果然是批評我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.97,0:18:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不對
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.27,0:18:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是愛的告白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.74,0:18:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼想都不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.81,0:18:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是我一直很在意你這一點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.94,0:18:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}與其說喜歡 應該說從前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.26,0:18:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你就一副親切的好孩子的模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.38,0:18:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}心底卻藏著冷漠的一角
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.26,0:18:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以我想嘩啦啦掀開你那層好孩子的皮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.17,0:18:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你那是什麼意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.85,0:18:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你不懂我的愛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.77,0:18:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}高坂同學有點扭曲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.41,0:18:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.51,0:18:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.38,0:18:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.79,0:18:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}高坂同學想看這幅景象的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.63,0:18:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}跟想看有點不同
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.99,0:19:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是想做和別人不同的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.40,0:19:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}地面好像星空
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.55,0:19:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那是縣祭的光芒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.26,0:19:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你那麼在意塚本嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.10,0:19:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}才沒這回事 我們也不是那種關係
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.95,0:19:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是那種啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.81,0:19:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.95,0:19:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}話說 像這樣在縣祭時爬山這種蠢事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.11,0:19:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}應該不會有人做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.41,0:19:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.65,0:19:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我想久美子能理解我的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.07,0:19:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不會勉強自己和不感興趣的人交朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.10,0:19:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}透過和別人一樣來獲得心理安慰 太蠢了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.72,0:19:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我想反抗那理所當然形成的小團體
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.93,0:19:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然很難全部理解
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.92,0:19:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是你能理解吧 這含義不明的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.37,0:20:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 我能明白高坂同學的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.38,0:20:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}麗奈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.73,0:20:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}麗奈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.26,0:20:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我想成為獨一無二的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.15,0:20:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不想和別人一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.34,0:20:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以我吹奏小號
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.51,0:20:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為了與眾不同
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.77,0:20:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好像被她吸引住了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.22,0:20:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這一瞬間 就算為她獻上生命我也毫不介意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.12,0:20:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}吹小號就能成為獨一無二嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.85,0:20:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.97,0:20:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不斷練習不斷進步 就能越來越獨特
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.25,0:20:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不會當孤芳自賞的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.60,0:20:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}而會成為真正的獨一無二
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.67,0:21:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}久美子的個性果然很差
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.10,0:21:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.99,0:21:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好了 吹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.90,0:21:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}國三時在餞別會上吹過的那首
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.74,0:21:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那首？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.61,0:21:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.08,0:21:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.10,0:23:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.43,0:23:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們度過了一段如同夢境般不可思議的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.09,0:23:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}接著
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.20,0:23:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那麼試音開始
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.93,0:23:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}新的一曲奏響了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.93,0:23:39.98,Title,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\bord0.5\pos(1080,570)\fad(830,0)} 待續
